snippet.title: Chicken Run (PS1/DC/PC) Trailer
snippet.description:
My 500th video

The game published by Eidos and developed by Blitz Games based on the movie by Dreamworks, Aardman and Pathé.

"All the fun of the film - revisit the most hilarious scenes! Play as Ginger, Rocky, Nick, and Fetcher in some of the craziest escape plans ever. It's time you helped those chickens fly the coop! If you enjoyed the film, you will love this 3D Action Adventure game. Available on PC CD-ROM, PlayStation and Dreamcast."
